(153, 1, '2014-09-24 00:40:33', '2014-09-24 00:40:33', '<p style="margin:0px"><img class="alignleft wp-image-635 size-thumbnail" src="http://localhost/jpmwordpress/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/london-me1-150x150.jpg" alt="" width="150" height="150" /></p>\r\n<div style="margin: 0px 0px 20px 170px;">\r\n\r\n<strong>Hi, I''m John Paul Moran</strong> <i>AKA ArtworkJPM</i>. In 2006 I started working full time as a Mac Artworker in the print industry. After learning all about creating and amending artwork I decided to progress into web design. After attending several college courses, online courses, I landed an internship as a junior web designer. In 2013 I started working full time in Web design and finally started getting paid!\r\n  \r\n  <strong>What is my ideal job?</strong><br>\r\n  I love working with HTML, CSS, JS and I love to learn new things. I am currently working in the travel industry and would like to carry on in this industry - however if a job came up to work for an interesting company in a different industry I''d be interested. I love creating graphics and working in a team. \r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<h1 class="entry-title">Work history gallery:</h1>\r\n<p class="no-bottom">(hover mouse for description)</p>\r\n[gallery type="rectangular" columns="1" ids="230,169,231,232,175,174,177,233,181,234"]', 'About me', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'about-me', '', '', '2014-10-09 16:33:16', '2014-10-09 16:33:16', '', 0, 'http://localhost/jpmwordpress//?page_id=153', 0, 'page', '', 0),
