(208, 1, '2015-09-17 12:06:59', '2015-09-17 12:06:59', 'If we say 100% is knowing everything, here is my verdict on my skills...\r\n\r\n[row]\r\n\r\n[column lg="6" md="6" sm="12" xs="12" ]\r\n\r\n<a href="http://localhost/jpmwordpress/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/pslogo2.jpg"><img class="bottompad alignleft wp-image-240 size-full" src="http://localhost/jpmwordpress/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/pslogo2.jpg" alt="photoshop" width="80" height="78" /></a>[progressbar value="95" class="photoshop" barstyle="progress-striped active" label="Adobe Photoshop"]\r\n\r\nI started using Photoshop at University and haven''t stopped, I''ve even helped the Police solve crimes with my Photoshop skills\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href="http://localhost/jpmwordpress/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/Adobe_Illustrator_Icon_CS6-copy.jpg"><img class="bottompad alignleft wp-image-222 size-full" src="http://localhost/jpmwordpress/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/Adobe_Illustrator_Icon_CS6-copy.jpg" alt="Adobe_Illustrator_Icon_CS6 copy" width="80" height="78" /></a>[progressbar value="85"  class="illustrator" barstyle="progress-striped active" label="Adobe Illustrator"]\r\n\r\nI''ve made lots of logos, cutting paths, buttons, mini illustrations and all kinds of lovely things on this baby.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href="http://localhost/jpmwordpress/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/indesign.jpg"><img class="bottompad alignleft wp-image-244 size-full" src="http://localhost/jpmwordpress/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/indesign.jpg" alt="indesign" width="80" height="78" /></a>[progressbar value="90" class="indesign"  barstyle="progress-striped active" label="Adobe Indesign"]\r\n\r\nI love Indesign for creating multipage artworks. Lets be honest - it kicks Quark''s ass. I''ve made calendars, brochures, product catalogues, large format exhibition graphics...too many to mention\r\n\r\n[/column]\r\n\r\n[column lg="6" md="6" sm="12" xs="12" ]\r\n\r\n<a href="http://localhost/jpmwordpress/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/HTML5_Logo_512.png"><img class="bottompad alignleft wp-image-248 size-full" src="http://localhost/jpmwordpress/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/HTML5_Logo_512.png" alt="" width="80" height="80" /></a>[progressbar value="80" class="htmlfive"  barstyle="progress-striped active" label="HTML, HTML5"]\r\n\r\nI started learning html back in 2007 when I made a my own website and some small business websites. Since html 5 came out I''ve used the new semantics like &lt;header&gt;, &lt;footer&gt;, &lt;article&gt;, and &lt;section&gt; for some static pages.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href="http://localhost/jpmwordpress/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/css3-logo.png"><img class="bottompad alignleft wp-image-254 size-full" src="http://localhost/jpmwordpress/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/css3-logo.png" alt="" width="80" height="80" /></a>[progressbar value="85" class="cssthree"  barstyle="progress-striped active" label="CSS, CSS3"]\r\n\r\nIt took me a while to get my head around using CSS, especially like Pseudo-classes, CSS Combinators (eg descendant, child ), postitioning...but I managed to understand it, mostly through doing projects and using websites like <a href="http://www.w3schools.com" target="_blank">www.w3schools.com</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href="http://localhost/jpmwordpress/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/wp.jpg"><img class="bottompad alignleft wp-image-257 size-full" src="http://localhost/jpmwordpress/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/wp.jpg" alt="" width="80" height="80" /></a>[progressbar value="75" class="wpskills"  barstyle="progress-striped active" label="Wordpress Development"]\r\n\r\nFirst time I used Wordpress I didn''t like it too much, "posts" or "pages"? what do I use? Now, I love it. Its so fast, free and a great introduction to PHP. I''ve made lots of small business sites on Wordpress and of course, this site.\r\n\r\n[/column]\r\n[/row]\r\n\r\n[well type=""]<br class="osc" /><br class="osc" /><strong>Currently learning...</strong>\r\n\r\n[row]\r\n\r\n[column lg="6" md="6" sm="12" xs="12" ]\r\n\r\n<br class="osc" />\r\n<a href="http://localhost/jpmwordpress/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/javascript_logo_.png"><img class="bottompad alignleft wp-image-264 size-full" src="http://localhost/jpmwordpress/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/javascript_logo_.png" alt="" width="80" height="80" /></a>[progressbar value="25" class="jsskills"  barstyle="progress-striped active" label="JavaScript"]\r\n\r\nI''ve completed the JavaScript course on <a title="code academy" href="http://www.codecademy.com" target="_blank">Code Academy</a>, attended several <a title="codebar" href="http://codebar.io/" target="_blank">Codebar </a>events. I''m getting to grips with JavaScript and learning how to make interesting things\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href="http://localhost/jpmwordpress/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/jquery-logo1.jpg"><img class="bottompad alignleft wp-image-276 size-full" src="http://localhost/jpmwordpress/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/jquery-logo1.jpg" alt="" width="80" height="80" /></a>[progressbar value="15" class="jqskills"  barstyle="progress-striped active" label="jQuery - <em>write less, do more</em>"]\r\n\r\nI''ve dambled in this library, used some slider galleries like <a title="Nivo slider" href="http://dev7studios.com/plugins/nivo-slider/" target="_blank">Nivo</a> and <a title="wow slider" href="http://wowslider.com/" target="_blank">Wow</a>, and tweaked some jQuery to alter behaviour of an object. Right now I''m doing the <a title="code academy" href="http://www.codecademy.com" target="_blank">Code Academy</a> course and aim to build some animations / moving web graphics.\r\n\r\n[/column]\r\n\r\n[column lg="6" md="6" sm="12" xs="12" ]\r\n\r\n<a href="http://localhost/jpmwordpress/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/php_01.png"><img class="bottompad alignleft wp-image-278 size-full" src="http://localhost/jpmwordpress/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/php_01.png" alt="" width="80" height="78" /></a>[progressbar value="15" class="php"  barstyle="progress-striped active" label="PHP"]\r\n\r\nI''ve read books on this, used it in Wordpress to change some functions. I am learning this powerful language and trying to use my new skills for projects I undertake.\r\n\r\n[/column]\r\n[/row]<br class="osc" />\r\n[/well]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Skills Estimator', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '195-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-09-17 12:06:59', '2015-09-17 12:06:59', '', 195, 'http://localhost/jpmwordpress//195-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
