(282, 1, '2014-09-26 21:53:29', '2014-09-26 21:53:29', 'Whilst working at Printwell I was tasked with redesigning the <a title="Printbubble" href="http://www.printbubble.co.uk/" target="_blank">Printbubble home page</a> and product pages. The site uses a rather dated, unknown CMS that proved to be difficult to understand at first. In the end I managed to redesign the home page, it was my first hand coded from scratch job I done for an established brand.\r\n\r\nI learnt a lot about HTML and CSS on this project.\r\n\r\n[button style="btn-default btn-lg btn" type="link" target="true" title="view printbubble website" link="http://www.printbubble.co.uk/"]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[gallery type="rectangular" ids="295,285,284,283"]', 'Printbubble website redesign', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'printbubble-website-redesign', '', '', '2014-10-08 11:27:38', '2014-10-08 11:27:38', '', 0, 'http://localhost/jpmwordpress//?p=282', 0, 'post', '', 0),
