(549, 1, '2014-10-06 19:32:14', '2014-10-06 19:32:14', '<h1><img class="wp-image-182 size-full alignleft" src="http://localhost/jpmwordpress/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/logo.gif" alt="" width="235" height="97" /></h1>\r\n<h1>Printwell UK Ltd</h1>\r\n[button style="btn-default btn-lg" icon="fa fa-file-o" align="left" type="link" target="true" title="Reference pdf" link="http://localhost/jpmwordpress/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/j-moran-printwell-reference.pdf"]\r\n<blockquote>[iconheading type="h1" style="fa fa-quote-left"][/iconheading]I highly recommend John Moran as a candidate for employment. John was employed by Printwell UK Ltd as a designer and online administrator as of 2nd September 2013 - 18th May 2014 and has continued to work on a freelance basis to current date.\r\n\r\nJohn has very good communication skills, in addition he is reliable and computer literate. John can work independently and is able to follow through to ensure that the job/task gets done. He is flexible and willing to work on any project that is assigned to him.\r\n\r\nJohn would be a tremendous asset for your company and has my highest recommendation. If you have any further questions with regards to his background or qualifications, please do not hesitate to contact me.\r\n[iconheading type="h1" style="fa fa-quote-right"][/iconheading]\r\n\r\n[well type=""]Nisreen Ghor\r\nCompany Secretary\r\n0208 687 9243\r\nNisreen.ghor@printwell.co.uk<br class="osc" />[/well]</blockquote>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h1><a href="http://localhost/jpmwordpress/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/dd1.jpg"><img class="alignleft wp-image-551 size-full" src="http://localhost/jpmwordpress/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/dd1.jpg" alt="dd1" width="317" height="80" /></a></h1>\r\n<h1>Discount Displays</h1>\r\n[button style="btn-default btn-lg" icon="fa fa-file-o" align="left" type="link" target="true" title="Reference pdf" link="http://localhost/jpmwordpress/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/John-Moran-discount-display-reference_smaller.pdf"]\r\n<blockquote>[iconheading type="h1" style="fa fa-quote-left"][/iconheading]\r\n\r\nJohn Moran worked for Discount Displays from June until November 2008 as a Mac Artworker\r\nand Large format print operator.\r\n\r\nHis duties involved designing and preparing artwork for print and setting and operating large format\r\nprint machines.\r\n\r\nHe was proficient in the following software applications. Adobe Photoshop, Adobe Illustrator, Adobe\r\nIndesign, Quark Xpress\r\n\r\nI always found John to be an honest and conscientious worker.[iconheading type="h1" style="fa fa-quote-right"][/iconheading]\r\n\r\n[well type=""]Martin Deane\r\nStudio and Print Manager\r\nDiscount Displays\r\n31 - 35 Wortley Road, Croydon, Surrey, CR0 3EB\r\nsales@discountdisplays.co.uk\r\nTel: 0844 800 1020[/well]</blockquote>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h1><a href="http://localhost/jpmwordpress/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/sg_small.jpg"><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-587" src="http://localhost/jpmwordpress/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/sg_small.jpg" alt="sg_small" width="80" height="80" /></a>Service Graphics</h1>\r\n[button style="btn-default btn-lg" icon="fa fa-file-o" align="left" type="link" target="true" title="Reference pdf" link="http://localhost/jpmwordpress/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Reference-of-Employment.pdf"]\r\n<blockquote>[iconheading type="h1" style="fa fa-quote-left"][/iconheading]\r\n\r\nTo whom it may concern\r\n\r\nThis is a reference letter to confirm that John Moran, date of birth 07/07/1979 worked for Jupiter Display, which was a division of Service graphics.\r\n\r\nHe worked from 11/11/05 - 15/06/08 as a Mac Operator. His duties were to set up artwork for printing on the large format machines, run the large format machines and do occasional design and amending for artwork using Adobe Creative Suite and Quark. He also helped out in general production duties, this included some installation of graphics on location and some work in the mounting department.\r\n\r\nInitially John started as a trainee and progressed to become Mac Artworker.\r\n\r\nJohn was a good, reliable employee and I wish him luck in his career.\r\n\r\nYours faithfully\r\n\r\n[iconheading type="h1" style="fa fa-quote-right"][/iconheading][well type=""]Graham Page\r\nOperations Director\r\nService Graphics\r\nChessington\r\nLondon\r\n[/well]</blockquote>', 'References', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'references', '', '', '2014-10-07 16:34:44', '2014-10-07 16:34:44', '', 0, 'http://localhost/jpmwordpress//?page_id=549', 0, 'page', '', 0),
